Stage 4 of 8: See the World, levels 5 to 30

The "areas" command catalogs every region with level ranges. Characters
up to level 10 already know the newbie-area wayshards, and touching new
shards opens fast travel as you explore. Pick up quests for structured
goals and bonus experience.

Above level 5 death costs 10 percent of your experience on hand. Your
corpse keeps your gear, the church will bring you back, and other
players can avenge you to restore what you lost.

